data.description: Check out this spacious, but cozy feeling home that is located in the very desirable Castle Rock community! 5 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, living room with inviting fireplace, dining room, gorgeous hardwood floors throughout. Upgraded kitchen with gorgeous wood cupboards includes stainless steel  appliances. Dbl pane windows throughout, inviting front porch,  partially finished basement has a big finished bathroom with a jacuzzi tub. Big beautiful back deck for entertaining that overlooks a secluded, wooded, backyard. Home built in 2005 on existing concrete basement.  2 car garage with storage. All of this in a quiet cul-de-sac. Virtually no yard maintenance, move-in ready and close to I-5?
